Package: LLM_EnrichViz
Title: LLM-Powered Multi-Method Enrichment Analysis and Visualization
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Your", "Name", email = "your.email@example.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0000-0000-0000"))
  )
Description: Performs comprehensive gene set enrichment analyses using four
    complementary methods: ORA (Over-Representation Analysis), GSEA (Gene Set
    Enrichment Analysis), GSVA (Gene Set Variation Analysis), and ROAST
    (Rotation-based gene set testing). Each analysis is independently
    interpreted by a Large Language Model (LLM) chosen from Gemini, OpenAI
    (GPT), Anthropic (Claude), or DeepSeek. A multi-agent system collects
    per-method insights and synthesizes them into an integrated mechanistic
    model with network visualization and an automated HTML report.
